UNITED STATES ex rel. Salvatore GIACOBBI, Appellant, v. J. Arthur FLUCKEY, Director of Immigration, Appellee. No. 240. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. March 25, 1940. Rulison, Parker & Ryan and William Ryan, all of Syracuse, N. Y., for appellant. Ralph L. Emmons, U. S. Atty., of Bing-hamton, N. Y., and Andrew J. Culick, Asst. U. S. Atty., of Amsterdam, N. Y., for ap-pellee.

Before L. HAND, CHASE, and CLARK, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order, 32 F.Supp. 508, affirmed.
